@baude thanks for tagging me!

@usdn1 any chance you could try with the latest version of the passt package available for Debian (0.0~git20250919.623dbf6-1)? It's compatible with Podman 5.4.2 as well and will happily install on Trixie as well.

We fixed a few issues meanwhile, and we tend to only support latest upstream versions here. I don't have a specific fix in mind, though. We don't routinely test things with `nc`, but I might as well try that kind of loop if the problem persists.
